{
  "stem": "7455.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That if the church is hit, we're finished because it's [? hell. ?] My father was exhausted from saving the stuff.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he kept saying, I couldn't save my house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I couldn't save my house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And when there was a period when the planes retreated momentarily, he walked to the gate of the church and stood there, and saw our house collapse.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The roofs cave in and tongues of flame coming out of the windows.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he wept, and he cried, smudge with his soots, broken up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother, [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Munio, ?] went over to him, embraced him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, daddy, don't cry for the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If we will survive this war, and we'll be all together, a family, nobody will be missing, we'll consider ourselves very lucky people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father said, but what will you do when nightfall comes and you'll have no place to put your head down, no home to go into?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was thinking my brother had that wisdom of-- that he knew what's com-- he felt that-- he felt that danger is coming.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Ukrainians, their homes, our neighbors', was burned down, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But their heart was light.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They anticipated that their benefactor will come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans will march, and they'll have their land back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And during quiet moments, they sang songs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a foreboding of tragedy and trouble.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they were civil with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were able to-- we-- for three days, we were laying down blankets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whenever we heard pla-- airplanes coming and the whistle of the bombs coming, we shriveled up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister and I were lying down on a blanket, and I felt, what do I have, a rock in my pocket?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What is it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Those were our hip bones.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
